Description: Aptura GNOME desktop integration
 Installs Aptura's GNOME integration, desktop launchers, and utility hooks.
 The default desktop stays close to upstream GNOME while adding Aptura
 branding, privacy-minded defaults, firmware visibility, power controls,
 recovery-oriented tools, and a local system health check.
